rComments: Amazing prof. By far the best I've ever had in all my years of university. You have to go to lectures since her slides don't have much information but she is an amazing, hilarious, thought provoking speaker and there is never a dull moment in class. She will also tell you exactly what is on midterms/exams. It was a privilege to attend her classes.

She comes off as nice in class, but makes no accommodations for students. She has no office hours and does not try to make up for that. If you expect to have no questions or concerns, she is a good professor.

Amazing lecturer!!! Would 100% take again. She gives a lot of context information to make everyone understand concepts better, and gives many hilarious examples. She is very clear on what will be on the exams. 10/10 loved her!
